        "message": "=<p>Hi {{ $json.Lead_Name }},</p>\n<p>A property just came available that fits what you told us you were looking for.</p>\n<p><strong>Property:</strong> {{ $json.Property_Name }}<br>\n<strong>Area:</strong> {{ $json.Area }}<br>\n<strong>Price:</strong> {{ $json.Price }}<br>\n<strong>Bedrooms:</strong> {{ $json.Bedrooms }}</p>\n<p>{{ $json.Description }}</p>\n<p>Interested in a viewing? Book a time here: https://cal.com/damii/property-viewing</p>\n<p>Looking forward to hearing from you.</p>\n\n\n\n",
        "options": {
